	     <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform"><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=120505"><span id="Scholar">emleoi</span></a><br /><b><span id="Scholar">Scholar</span></b><br /><span id="notbold">17 posts<br /><span id="notbold">Score:</span> Decent [3.42]</td><td valign=top class="mform" width="100%"><p>MUST HAVE FOR ANY CASTER!<br/>The Flowing ThoughtI makes a HUGE difference.&nbsp;&nbsp;This is an easy and excellent quest.  Found all items in the bazaar (Bristlebane server). Completed on 9/15/03.  We watched prices for about a week and picked up pieces when we saw them low.<br/>Here's what we paid for the items (prices are in platinum)<br/>* Demi-Sec Champagne - 40<br/>* Mistletoe Cutting Sickle - 1250<br/>* Golden Idol of Tunare -120<br/>* Blessed Fishing Rod - 950<br/>* Star Ruby Encrusted Stein - <br/>* Ceremonial Solstice Robe - 800<br/>* Lotus Pie - 30<br/>* Misty Thicket Picnic - 7<br/>* Lucky Cabbage -40<br/>If you're a caster, you need this item!  Imagine the stats with an augmentation from LDON.  You might as well augment it since it's no drop anyway.<br/><br/>Verahshee 51 Wizzy<br/>Arwenne 51 Chanter</p>&nbsp;<br /></td></tr>
